## Convenciones de naming

```
tests/Unit/Workspaces/LimitServiceTest.php
tests/Feature/Workspaces/CreateWorkspaceTest.php
tests/Feature/Workspaces/NestedWorkspaceTest.php   ← ->group('pgsql')
tests/E2E/WorkspaceCollaborationFlowTest.php
```

Cada test describe una acción clara:
```php
test('creates workspace with correct ltree path')
test('throws depth exceeded when plan limit reached')
test('orphans children when parent is deleted')
test('guest cannot create workspace')
```

