## Referencia cruzada por etapa

Cada stage MDC especifica qué tests implementar.
Esta guía es el estándar que todos los stages siguen.

| Etapa | Unit tests | Feature tests | E2E tests |
|---|---|---|---|
| 04 Auth | TokenService | login, register, refresh, logout, me | OnboardingFlow |
| 09 Enterprises | — | CRUD, invitations, roles | OnboardingFlow |
| 10 Subscriptions | LimitService | limits, overrides, usage | — |
| 12 Workspaces | — | CRUD, ltree, orphaned | WorkspaceCollaborationFlow |
| 14 Assets | — | upload, references, retention | — |
| 16 Rooms | — | CRUD, participants, tokens | RoomSessionFlow |
| 18 Conversations | — | messages, visibility, threading | RoomSessionFlow |
| 21 Streams | — | lifecycle, limits | StreamingFlow |
